# Code owners for release-critical paths. Combined with the `main` branch ruleset's
# "Require review from Code Owners", any PR touching these paths needs an approving review from one
# of the listed owners. See docs/release-flow.md.
#
# There is intentionally no catch-all `*` rule: all other source (wrappers/*, core/*, docs, ...)
# stays unowned and does NOT require these reviewers. CODEOWNERS is last-match-wins, so keep the
# patterns below non-overlapping.

# Bumping the version drives the auto-tag + release.
/gradle.properties        @satran004 @matiwinnetou @fabianbormann

# Protect the release pipeline and this gate itself from unreviewed changes.
/.github/workflows/       @satran004 @matiwinnetou @fabianbormann
/.github/CODEOWNERS       @satran004 @matiwinnetou @fabianbormann
